Set a textScale via mapView.setTextScale() and then subsequently change the render theme, this textScale is not applied and text appears very small.

The problem is in the DatabaseRenderer.java:

```
    float textScale = mapGeneratorJob.jobParameters.textScale;
    if (Float.compare(textScale, this.previousTextScale) != 0) {
        this.renderTheme.scaleTextSize(textScale);
        this.previousTextScale = textScale;
